OL,3,CMan in his 70s dies in collision with
OL,4,Ca car on village road
OL,6,FA man in his 70s has died in a crash
OL,7,Fin East Hendred in Oxfordshire.
OL,9,FThe pedestrian was walking on the A417
OL,10,FReading Road when a Volkswagen Golf
OL,11,Fcollided with him.
OL,13,FSouth Central Ambulance Service called
OL,14,FThames Valley Police on Thursday
OL,15,Fevening (9 April) at 7:20pm reporting
OL,16,Fa road accident.
OL,18,FThe man was pronounced dead at the
OL,19,Fscene.
