OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775920265
OL,3,CMan in his 70s dies in collision with
OL,4,Ca car on village road
OL,6,FHis family has been informed and will
OL,7,Fbe offered support by specially
OL,8,Ftrained officers.
OL,10,FNo arrests have been made as officers
OL,11,Fappeal for any witnesses to come
OL,12,Fforward and contact police.
OL,14,FInvestigating officer Detective
OL,15,FSergeant Oliver CahillSmith, from the
OL,16,FSerious Collision Investigation Unit,
OL,17,Fsaid: "First and foremost, our
OL,18,Fthoughts are with the loved ones of
OL,19,Fthe man who tragically lost his life
OL,20,Fin this collision.
OL,26,@yD@GOU
