CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775920265
OL,3,CMan in his 70s dies in collision with
OL,4,Ca car on village road
OL,6,FWe are investigating this collision as
OL,7,Fa priority and would urge anyone who
OL,8,Fwitnessed the incident to get in touch.
OL,10,FWe would particularly like to speak to
OL,11,Fdrivers who passed through the area
OL,12,Fbetween 7.10pm and 7.20pm, especially
OL,13,Fthose travelling west towards Wantage,
OL,14,Fas they may be able to provide witness
OL,15,Faccounts or relevant dashcam footage
OL,16,Fof the driving conditions at the time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
